Class LinHashMap<K,V>

Project2.LinHashMap<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,V>
public class LinHashMap<K,V> extends AbstractMap<K,V> implements Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,V>
This class provides hash maps that use the Linear Hashing algorithm. A hash table is created that is an expandable array-list of buckets.
